5000|$|Blend of <b>straight</b> <b>whiskeys</b> is {{a mixture}} of one or more <b>straight</b> <b>whiskeys</b> that either {{includes}} <b>straight</b> <b>whiskeys</b> produced in different U.S. states or coloring and flavoring additives (and possibly other approved [...] "blending materials"), or both, but does not contain grain neutral spirits.|$|R
5000|$|American [...] "blended whiskey" [...] {{is not to}} be {{confused}} with American whiskey labeled as a [...] "blend of straight whiskeys". A [...] "blend of straight whiskeys" [...] is a mixture of one or more <b>straight</b> <b>whiskeys</b> that either includes <b>straight</b> <b>whiskeys</b> produced in different U.S. states or coloring and flavoring additives (and possibly other approved [...] "blending materials"), or both, but does not contain neutral grain spirits.|$|R
